{"tid":768622,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[魔力新私服] 原味魔力 彷官服港台服","createTime":"2018-08-05T14:28:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-24T10:23:27.000Z","uid":6259,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"819a81321d7990fadeac8e2f5f89558dd2d9f0ed","tid":768622,"uid":6259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T14:28:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://originalcg.com/forum.php?mod=viewthread&amp;tid=29&amp;extra=\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Foriginalcg.com%2Fforum.php%3Fmod%3Dviewthread%26tid%3D29%26extra%3D&d=dgh%2BcIwXMOALXFQC76gWsozZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=29b469d2\" target=\"_blank\">http://originalcg.com/forum.php?mod=viewthread&amp;tid=29&amp;extra=</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://originalcg.com/forum.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Foriginalcg.com%2Fforum.php&d=dgh%2BcIwXMOALXFQC76gWsozZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=3bffb624\" target=\"_blank\">http://originalcg.com/forum.php</a><br />\nRC群: 27783527<br />\n<br />\n原味魔力堅持三不原則<br />\n1.不做變態服，2.不往不平衡發展，3.裝備武器寵物素質不隨意修正。<br />\n伺服器正式開放時間 : 2018/08/03(周五) 晚間19:00<br />\n<br />\n遊戲基本設置<br />\n經驗倍數<br />\n1-145\t2倍 / 上限 : 145<br />\n技能經驗<br />\n生產系<br />\n8倍 / 暫時開放到10 技<br />\n戰鬥系<br />\n8倍<br />\n修武／修防／鑑定／騎乘／炸彈轉化<br />\n8倍<br />\n<br />\n魔石價格  \t<br />\n1.5倍．顆堆疊數 3<br />\n<br />\n卡時上限\t<br />\n9小時<br />\n<br />\n技能學習費用\t<br />\n100G之技能  免費<br />\n其餘技能  一律半價<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">特色說明<br />\n<br />\n支援職業 : 爆彈師<br />\n<br />\n支援系統 :  原地登入 /一級提示 / 聲望查詢 / 寵物檔次計算 / 擺攤系統 / 魔攻魔防顯示 /可創目前官方最最新角色(底部圖參考)<br />\n<br />\n支援技能 : 追月 / 精神衝擊波 / 因果報應 / 虛死為上/ 羊頭狗肉 / 炸彈轉化/ 投擲<br />\n</span><br />\n  \t<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/05/222223_f54928ddb90269b7dcdf044cc3a99ba7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F05%2F222223_f54928ddb90269b7dcdf044cc3a99ba7.jpg&h=52238772&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.ne